{"name": "odoo14-addon-webservice", "metadata": {"name": "odoo14-addon-webservice", "version": "14.0.1.5.0", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 14.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/web-api", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo14-addon-component", "odoo14-addon-server-environment", "odoo"], "summary": "Provide unified way to handle external webservices configuration and calls.", "upload_time": 1698169480}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fweb--api-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/web-api\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/web-api/tree/14.0/webservice\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/web-api-14-0/web-api-14-0-webservice\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/web-api&target_branch=14.0\n    ```\n  maintainer-etobella: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/etobella.png?size=40px\n    :alt: etobella\n    :target: https://github.com/etobella\n    ```\n  maintainer-simahawk: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/simahawk.png?size=40px\n    :alt: simahawk\n    :target: https://github.com/simahawk\n    ```\n---\n\n# WebService\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:ae796f345a1c257df4f5f1e44b07bca6f2f3a9684662b7e2bbb7e5cceb628966\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nProvide unified way to handle external webservices configuration and calls.\n\nEach external webservice is represented - and configured - by a `webservice.backend` record.\nThe handling of the requests is delegated to adapters (special components).\nAt the moment, the only protocol supported by directly by this module is `HTTP`.\n\nAdditional protocols can be easily supported by adding more adapters.\n\nNevertheless, no matter which protocol you'll use,\ntechnically you'll have to always issue calls from the backend object.\nEg:\n\n> my_backend.call(\"GET\", \"any/endpoint\")\n> my_backend.call(\"POST\", \"any/endpoint\")\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/web-api/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/web-api/issues/new?body=module:%20webservice%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Creu Blanca\n- Camptocamp\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Enric Tobella \\<<mailto:etobella@creublanca.es>>\n- Simone Orsi \\<<mailto:simone.orsi@camptocamp.com>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nCurrent [maintainers](https://odoo-community.org/page/maintainer-role):\n\n{{ maintainer-etobella }} {{ maintainer-simahawk }}\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/web-api](https://github.com/OCA/web-api/tree/14.0/webservice) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.webservice.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.webservice.models.webservice_backend", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.webservice.models..webservice_backend", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.webservice.utils", "documentation": ["Copyright 2023 Camptocamp SA", "@author Simone Orsi <simahawk@gmail.com>", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [{"name": "odoo.addons.webservice.utils.sanitize_url_for_log", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "url", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "blacklisted_keys", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Sanitize url to avoid loggin sensitive data"]}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.webservice.tests.test_utils", "documentation": ["Copyright 2023 Camptocamp SA", "@author Simone Orsi <simahawk@gmail.com>", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.webservice.tests.test_utils.TestUtils", "bases": ["BaseCase"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.webservice.tests.test_utils.TestUtils.test_url_cleanup", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}]